  "title": "L2 Preschool Educator (Islandwide)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Design and execute curriculum and learning programs.</li>\n  <li>Foster strong relationships and collaborations with stakeholders.</li>\n  <li>Oversee family and community engagement initiatives.</li>\n  <li>Carry out daily caregiving duties.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Requirements:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Must hold at least a <strong>Diploma</strong> in one of the following:Early Childhood Education (ECH)<br>\nChild Psychology &amp; Early Education (CPEE)<br>\nEarly Childhood Studies (ECS)<br>\nEarly Childhood Development &amp; Education (ECDE)<br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>",
